messages.message: :aws: :lock: due to compliance requirement we removed the shared S3 key/secret to access dogfood drives in our code base, if you still need to make it work for your local env, please ~create S3 key set from your instabase aws account (reaching out to IT if you don't have aws access) and use your own key instead.~ find the key/secret pair in :1password: engineering team vault named `AWS S3DogfoodUser` and use the key saved there instead.
